TROUBLESHOOTING:
  Problem: OLED not showing
  → Check I2C connections (GPIO21/SDA, GPIO22/SCL)
  → Verify power to OLED (3.3V)
  → Scan for 0x3C address

  Problem: Voltage reading wrong
  → Measure actual voltage at GPIO35
  → Check divider resistor values (R1=100k, R2=10k)
  → Verify Zener is limiting to <3.3V

  Problem: Current reading incorrect
  → Check ACS712 power (5V on VCC)
  → Measure VOUT pin (should be ~2.5V at 0A)
  → Verify no shorts in current path

  Problem: Motor doesn't start
  → Check relay coil voltage (5V)
  → Verify GPIO12/GPIO13 going HIGH
  → Test relay manually with 5V battery

